f1f0e0b0b","tid":159663,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"根據香港法例第217章&lt;武器條例&gt;第4條 - 管有違禁武器:<br />\n<br />\n任何人管有違禁武器， 即屬犯罪， 可處罰款$10000及監禁3年。<br />\n<br />\n違禁武器的定義為:<br />\n<br />\n中國式飛鏢 /重力刀 / 重力操作鋼棒 / 指節套， 不論是否有尖釘及是否有刀刃 / 附有手柄的鐵鏈 / 彈簧鋼棒 / 任何以彈簧或 其他機械或 電動裝置露出刀刃的 刀 / 任何有刀刃或 尖端的 武器， 其設計是在 使用時以拳頭緊握手柄， 而刀刃或 尖端則從拳頭指縫間突出<br />\n<br />\n蝴蝶刀被視為重力刀 (利用gravity嚟開合既刀)之一種, 帶入香港 / 藏有 / 帶出街都係犯法嘅!"},{"pid":"5230414d73e66eb7a190f4d8d5e4a8646ffc65b3","tid":159663,"uid":380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"買把未開鋒咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717991ccf830d3b1265ccad7888c45b54c2b1420","tid":159663,"uid":68208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/6c0mx915\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6c0mx915&h=cc7018ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n興呀 都幾多人有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無敵海景<br />\n巴打喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af25ce1b66d1e7336fe15e01280e4346a2605fa3","tid":159663,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/6c0mx915\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6c0mx915&h=cc7018ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n興呀 都幾多人有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.